        },
        {
            "title": "積金評級：強積金4月暫時人均賺2.03萬元 有望收復3月份虧損",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">積金評級今早發表報告，指出截至22日止強積金在4月份暫時錄得約6.35%投資回報，人均約賺2.03萬元，有望收復3月份的虧損。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15925659-%e7%a9%8d%e9%87%91%e8%a9%95%e7%b4%9a%ef%bc%9a%e5%bc%b7%e7%a9%8d%e9%87%914%e6%9c%88%e6%9a%ab%e6%99%82%e4%ba%ba%e5%9d%87%e8%b3%ba2-03%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83-%e6%9c%89%e6%9c%9b%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a93%e6%9c%88",
